<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Restricted</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .path {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            color: #d63384;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .info {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .info strong {
            color: #0066cc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon">üö´</div>
        <h1>Access Restricted</h1>
        <p>This external URL is only available for the student interface.</p>
        
        {{#if requestedPath}}
        <div class="path">
            Requested: {{requestedPath}}
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        
        <div class="info">
            <strong>‚ÑπÔ∏è For Facilitators & Administrators:</strong>
            <p style="margin-top:0.5rem; margin-bottom:0;">
                Please access the facilitator dashboard and admin pages directly via localhost or your local network IP address.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
